            "id": "4564056",
            "title": "Enghouse Systems reports Q1 results",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Enghouse Systems <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20436180-enghouse-releases-first-quarter-results\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EGHSF\" title=\"Enghouse Systems Limited\">EGHSF</a></span>): Q1 Revenue of $120.1M.</li>\n<li>Recurring revenue, which includes SaaS and maintenance services, decreased by 3.8% to $84.6 million compared to $87.9 million in Q1 2025, and represents 70.4% of total revenue, as we continue to prioritize this revenue stream;</li>\n<li>Results from operating activities were $28.3 million compared to $31.0 million in Q1 2025;</li>\n<li>Net income was $17.5 million compared to $21.9 million in Q1 2025;</li>\n<li>Adjusted EBITDA decreased to $31.1 million compared to $33.1 million, while achieving a 25.9% margin;</li>\n<li>Net cash provided by operating activities, excluding changes in working capital and income taxes paid, was $31.4 million compared to $37.7 million in Q1 2025. Cash, cash equivalents and short-term investments were $260.2 million as at January 31, 2026.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
